# Task Manager

A modern, responsive task management application built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Features local storage persistence, interactive charts, and a clean user interface.

## Features

- ✅ **Task Management**: Add, edit, toggle completion, and delete tasks
- 🎯 **Priority System**: High, Medium, and Low priority levels
- 📊 **Visual Analytics**: Progress bar and doughnut chart with Chart.js
- 🔍 **Filtering**: View All, Pending, or Completed tasks
- 📈 **Sorting**: Sort by Newest, Oldest, A→Z, or Priority
- 💾 **Local Storage**: All data persists in browser localStorage
- 📱 **Responsive Design**: Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile
- ♿ **Accessible**: Screen reader friendly with proper ARIA labels
- 🎨 **Modern UI**: Clean, card-based design with smooth animations

## Technologies Used

- **HTML5**: Semantic markup with accessibility features
- **CSS3**: Modern styling with CSS Grid, Flexbox, and custom properties
- **Vanilla JavaScript**: ES6+ features, classes, and modules
- **Chart.js**: Interactive doughnut chart via CDN
- **LocalStorage API**: Client-side data persistence

## File Structure

ask-manager/
├── index.html # Main HTML file
├── css/
│ └── style.css # All styles and responsive design
├── js/
